body.prompt:
URGENT: New incident created. Please investigate immediately.

Incident: {{.entity.identifier}}
Title: {{.entity.title}}
Severity: {{.entity.properties.severity}}
Affected Service: {{.entity.relations.affected_service}}

Please:
1. Get details about the affected service
2. Check for recent deployments (last 48 hours)
3. Identify the service owner and on-call
4. Form a hypothesis about the root cause
5. Recommend immediate actions

Update the incident entity with your triage_summary and hypothesis fields.
